text:
Is there a solution to this yet? I'm having this issue as well when the icon is inside a repeater. The error is *missing {{ token }} value*. Here is my code:
```&lt;div class="row"&gt;
  {% for item in module.resource %}
  &lt;a href="{{ item.resource_link }}" target="_blank"&gt;
    {% icon name="{{ item.resource_icon.name }}" style="{{ item.resource_icon.type }}" unicode="{{ item.resource_icon.unicode }}" %}
  &lt;/a&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;{{ item.resource_description }}&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;a href="{{ item.resource_link }}" target="_blank"&gt;{{ item.resource_link_text }}&lt;/a&gt;
  {% endfor %}
&lt;/div&gt;```
